Guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City da ambaliyar ruwa
Ba kasafai ake samun matsanancin yanayi a Arizona ba, amma wannan shine abin da zai iya faruwa a mako mai zuwa lokacin da hanyar iska ta Hurricane Rosa ta tsallaka cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata don Arizona ta yamma zuwa kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran Rosa za ta hau kan Phoenix a ranar Talata, ta yi nisa da yammacin jiya saboda ruwan sama.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Phoenix ta rubuta a cikin wani tweet cewa "kawai guguwa goma ne kawai suka kasance cikin hadari ko kuma yanayi mai zafi a cikin nisan mil 200 daga Phoenix tun 1950!
Katrina (1967) wani guguwa ne da ke da nisan mil 40 daga iyakar AZ".
Sabbin tsarin da Cibiyar Guguwa ta Kasa ta tsara na hasashen ruwan sama inci biyu zuwa hudu, tare da yawan mutane da ke cikin Mogollon Rim a Arizona.
Sauran yankuna a cikin Desert Kudu maso Yamma ciki har da tsakiyar Rockies da Great Basin na iya samun 1 zuwa 2 inci, tare da wasu yankuna masu nisa har zuwa yiwuwar 4 inci.
Ga wadanda ke cikin hadarin ambaliyar ruwa, ruwan sama na iya zama alheri tun lokacin da yankin ya sha wahala.
Duk da cewa ambaliyar ruwa babbar damuwa ce, wasu na ganin ruwan sama zai amfane su tunda Kudu maso Yammacin kasar na fuskantar matsalar fari.
A cewar U.S. Drought Monitor, sama da kashi 40 na Arizona suna fama da mafi munin fari, na biyu mafi girma, "in ji weather.com.
Da farko, hanyar guguwar Rosa ta nufa ga yankin Baja California a Mexico.
Rosa, wanda ke da ƙarfin guguwa a safiyar Lahadi tare da iyakar iska 85 mph, yana da mil 385 a kudancin Punta Eugenia, Mexico kuma yana motsawa arewacin da mil 12 a kowace awa.
Guguwa tana fuskantar ruwan sanyi a cikin Pacific kuma saboda haka yana haifar da saukowa.
Saboda haka, ana sa ran za a yi ambaliyar ƙasa a Mexico a cikin ƙarfin guguwar wurare masu zafi da yamma ko yammacin ranar Litinin.
Ruwan sama a ko'ina cikin Mexico na iya zama mai yawa, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
"Ana sa ran samun ruwan sama inci 3 zuwa 6 daga Baja California zuwa Sonora arewa maso yamma, har zuwa inci 10, "in ji weather.com.
Rosa za ta yi nisa zuwa arewacin Mexico a matsayin guguwar da ta kai iyakar Arizona da safiyar Talata a matsayin guguwar da ta kai gajiya, sannan za ta zagaya Arizona da kudancin Utah da yammacin Talata.
"Babban haɗarin da ake tsammani daga Rosa ko kuma ɓarnar shine ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, Sonora ta arewa maso yamma, da kuma hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amurka, "in ji Cibiyar Guguwa ta Kasa.
Ana sa ran ruwan sama zai haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai barazana ga rayuka da kuma ambaliyar ƙasa a hamada, da kuma rushewar ƙasa a yankunan tsaunuka.
