Kanye West: Rapper ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye
Mawaki Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
Sanar da sauya sunansa a shafin Twitter a ranar Asabar, ya rubuta: Wannan mutumin an san shi da Kanye West.
Kanye West, mai shekara 41, an kira shi Ye na ɗan lokaci kuma ya yi amfani da wannan laƙabin a matsayin taken kundin waƙarsa na takwas wanda aka buga a watan Yuni.
Wannan juyin juya halin ya faru ne yayin da ta fito a wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Asabar da dare inda ake sa ran za ta fitar da sabon kundin ta Yandhi.
Ta maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande wacce ta soke fitowarta a cikin wasan kwaikwayon saboda "matsalar motsin rai", in ji mahaliccin wasan kwaikwayon.
A baya, Kanye West ya ce sunan yana da ma'ana ta addini kuma yana da gajeren suna ga sunansa na yanzu.
"Na yi imani ye kalma ce da aka fi samu a cikin Linjila kuma tana nufin ku", in ji Kanye West a farkon wannan shekarar yayin tattauna taken kundin waƙarsa da mai gabatar da rediyo Big Boy.
"Saboda haka ni ma kai ne, ni ma mu ne, mu ne mu".
Ya canza daga Kanye wanda ke nufin abu daya, zuwa Ye - hoton da ke nuna nagarta da mugunta da kuma kuskurenmu da komai.
Wannan kundin ya fi nuna ainihin kamanninmu.
Ya kasance daya daga cikin shahararrun mawaƙa na rap wanda ya canza sunansa.
Sean Combs an san shi da sunaye daban-daban kamar Puff Daddy, P. Diddy ko Diddy amma a wannan shekara ya sanar da cewa ya fi son sunayen Love da Brother Love.
Tsohon abokin aikin Kanye West, JAY-Z, zai iya karɓar wannan tare da ko ba tare da alamun rubutu da manyan haruffa ba.
Shugaban Mexico, AMLO ya sha alwashin ba zai yi amfani da sojoji kan fararen hula ba
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya sha alwashin cewa ba zai yi amfani da sojoji ba a kan fararen hula yayin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kisan gillar da aka yi wa daliban.
AMLO ya yi alkawari a Plaza Tlatelolco ranar Asabar cewa "ba zai taba amfani da sojoji ba wajen dakile 'yan Mexico".
Sojoji sun harbe fararen hula da ke zanga-zangar lumana a dandalin a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968 wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar fararen hula 300 yayin da 'yan daliban hagu suka fara gangami a duk faɗin Latin Amurka.
AMLO ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin wata-wata ga waɗanda ke karatu da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin damar samun ilimi na janyo matasa shiga cikin 'yan daba.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI.
"Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa a fannin ilimin kere kere saboda kasar Sin tana kara shiga cikin wannan fannin", in ji mai saka jari kuma mai ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan ra'ayi ya bayyana ne bayan da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi sanarwa game da ilimin kere kere duk da cewa Amurka kanta gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabarar dabarun kere kere.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a bara da nufin zama ta farko a cikin kirkire-kirkire na wucin gadi a shekarar 2030.
"Sau biyu na binciken AI kyakkyawan farawa ne, saboda sauran ƙasashe sun yi nisa da Amurka kuma muna son samun ci gaba a cikin AI", in ji Lee.
 Ta hanyar ninka kudaden, za a iya kara damar samun babban ci gaba na Artificial Intelligence (AI) a Amurka, Lee ya ce a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Littafin Lee mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and New World Order an buga shi a wannan watan ne daga Houghton Mifflin Harcout wanda shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures wanda ya zuba jari a wani babban kamfanin kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin ilimin kere kere wanda ya doke dan wasan Othello na Amurka wanda ya kasance a saman sa'ad da yake karatun a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon. Daga baya, ya zama mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban Google na China.
Lee ya san gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka kamar Robot Challenge na Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Harkokin Kasuwanci kuma yana son sanin lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba don ya iya gano sabbin baiwa.
Lee ya ce, "masu bincike a Amurka suna aiki sosai don samun tallafin gwamnati".
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke daukar shugabannin ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun dauki manyan mutane daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen tallafawa ayyukan leken asirin ta.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da katin kore ta atomatik ga waɗanda suka kammala karatun digirin digirgir a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa AI na gaba a watan Yulin 2017.
Lee ya ce, "Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da kudade ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence da nufin tattara abokan tarayya daga masana'antu da ilimi.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da saka hannun jari na dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
NSF tana saka sama da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara a cikin binciken AI.
A halin yanzu, dokar Amurka da ke neman kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa don Ilimin Artificial ba ta bayyana ba a cikin watanni da suka gabata.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar neman sauya sunan kasar
'Yan Macedonia sun gudanar da kuri'ar raba gardama a ranar Lahadi don yanke shawarar sauya sunan zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia.
