A cikin Bolivia da ke kewaye da ƙasar, ƙwaƙwalwar ajiyar asarar bakin teku ga Chile a cikin rikici mai tsanani a karni na 19 har yanzu yana da kyau - kamar yadda ake son sake tafiya a cikin Pacific Ocean.
Wannan fata na iya zama mafi girma a wannan karni, saboda Bolivia har yanzu tana jiran hukuncin Kotun Duniya na 1 ga Oktoba bayan shekaru biyar na tattaunawa.
