Tsohon shugaban kasar Eduardo Rodríguez Veltzé, wakilin Bolivia a Hague, ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa yanke hukuncin kotu yana da sauri.
A ranar Litinin za ta kawo Bolivia "babbar dama don bude sabuwar zamanin dangantaka da Chile" da kuma damar "kawo karshen shekaru 139 na rikici don kyautatawa juna", in ji ta.
