LeBron zai fara buga wa Lakers wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
A yanzu haka dai masu sha'awar LeBron James sun yi ta jiran ganin ya fara bugawa Los Angeles Lakers wasa.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a san tsawon lokacin da zai yi a wasan ba.
"Zai kasance fiye da daya da kuma kasa da minti 48", Walton ya ce a kan official Lakers website.
Mai gabatar da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya ce James zai iya buga wasa a cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan horo a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasanni shida kafin Lakers.
"Ba na bukatar wani wasa kafin kakar domin shirya a wannan mataki na aiki", ya ce.
Lokaci na taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara gangamin gangamin gaggawa a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na taron Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka riƙe kuri'un tabbatarwa don zaɓinsa don cike gurbin a Kotun Tarayya, Trump yana da niyyar samun goyon baya don zaɓen tsakiyar zangon da ke tafe saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar asarar ikon Majalisa lokacin da aka yanke shawarar zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai kasance kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling a West Virginia a karfe 7 na dare ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai gudanar da shari'ar wannan makon ga dan takarar kotun tarayya Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tashin hankali kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da tabbatar da kuri'ar majalisar dattijai da ake sa ran za a yi mako guda a ciki yayin binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan taro na gaggawa shi ne taimakawa 'yan Republican su samu ci gaba a gaban zaben Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa na Trump ya ce gangamin gangamin biyar a mako mai zuwa na nufin karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar sa don haka shugaban zai je jihohi da dama a cikinmu a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ba a bayyana sunansa ba.
An shirya shi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare na iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da ya kada a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke bin sa a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey har da shugaban ya zo don tallafa masa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: 'Yan wasan Amurka sun nuna karfin gwiwa wajen ganin an ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a wasan da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasa uku, wasan kusa da yammacin Asabar shine watakila abin da gasar Ryder ta buƙaci.
Motsa jiki shine wani ra'ayi na wasanni wanda shine wani abu da aka ƙirƙira amma yana da gaske da 'yan wasa suka gaskata, kuma mafi mahimmanci a cikin wasanni kamar wannan.
To, ina ne wannan lokacin yake yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida da amfani da kuma yanzu yana da maki hudu, don haka muna kawo kadan a cikin man fetur, ina ganin", Jordan Spieth ya ce kamar yadda ya yi tafiya a karshen rana.
Turai tana da fifiko, maki hudu a gaba da maki 12 a raga.
'Yan wasan Amurka, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin suna da ɗan ci gaba da jin ƙarfafawa, ba wai kawai daga Spieth da Justin Thomas da ke wasa tare duk rana ba kuma kowannensu yana da maki uku daga cikin huɗu.
Spieth ya nuna wasan mai guba daga farkon zuwa kore kuma ya zama misali ga sauran 'yan wasan.
Muryar farin ciki ta kara da karfi yayin da ya ci gaba da tafiya, yana yin rawar jiki mai mahimmanci don daidaita maki hudu lokacin da shi da Thomas suka rage bayan maki biyu.
Gwanin da ya yi wanda ya ba su nasara a rami na 15 an yi masa murna da irin wannan murna, wanda ya gaya maka cewa ya yi imanin cewa har yanzu Amurkawa suna fada.
"Kawai ka yi aiki tukuru ka damu da wasan ka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da duk 'yan wasan ke da shi a yanzu.
Ramin 18 don nuna iko.
'Yan wasa biyu da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin gasar Ryder da babu wanda zai iya jayayya da shi.
Wasu 'yan wasa sun yi wasa da wasu 'yan wasa da suka fito daga Turai, amma sun yi wasa da maki hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba su yi kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi ba a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma sun kuma guje wa bogi a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma ramuka tara na karshe a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan tsawon lokaci da kuma yadda magoya bayan suka nuna da kuma nunawa shine tabbacin cewa su 'yan wasan da za a ci a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasan da ya fi shahara wajen hana yiwuwar cin nasarar Turai a lokacin faduwar rana a Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau su kasance a cikin rami daban-daban.
Duk da haka, magana game da nasarar ƙungiyar Turai ta yi wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun sauƙaƙa aikin Sergio Garcia, gwarzon 'yan wasa huɗu da safe, lokacin da aka haɗa shi da Alex Noren.
Wani bogi da biyu a ramuka tara na farko sun kori dan wasan Spain da kuma dan wasan Sweden.
Duk da haka, a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka.
Hudu da 'yan wasa huɗu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallo kusa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da aka bayar da waɗanda ba a ba su ba da dabarun da za su iya canzawa a cikin ƙiftawar ido.
Turai ta yi fice sosai a matsayin kungiya kuma ta yi nisa a rana ta ƙarshe amma wannan zaman na hudu ya kuma nuna cewa Amurka tana da ƙarfin hali wanda mutane da yawa suka yi shakkarsa, gami da magoya bayan gida.
Kungiyar Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup
Turai ta samu nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan da ta tashi daga wasan kwallon kafa hudu da 'yan wasa hudu da ci 10 da 6 akan Amurka.
Manyan 'yan wasan biyu, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun ci gaba da cin nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke gwagwarmaya don kawo nasarar su a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Kungiyar Turai karkashin jagorancin Thomas Bjorn ta nemi rike kambun da ta kwace a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, inda ta doke Amurkawa da suka cika da sihiri a wasan da suka buga da safe da kwallon hudu, inda suka tashi da ci 3-1.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta ba da ƙarin gasa a wasan 'yan wasa huɗu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rufe rata ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki 8 daga cikin 12 a wasan da ta buga a ranar Lahadi domin rike kofin.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta fara zama 'yar Turai da ta ci kwallaye hudu a jere a lokacin da ita da Molinari, wanda ake kira "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban sha'awa, su ne na biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu a cikin wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon hudu, sai suka ci gaba da doke Woods da sabon dan wasan Amurka, Bryson Dechambeau a wasan 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kwarewarsa amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 da aka buga a raga hudu da 'yan wasa hudu kuma a jere bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda bai yi wasa ba a lokacin safiya na wasan kwallon kafa hudu, ya sake komawa tare da Henrik Stenson a cikin wasan hudu don kayar da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka a 2&1 - suna matsayi na ɗaya da uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta da sa'a a ranar da ta kwanta a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Masu cin kofin duniya sau uku, Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun zama maki biyu ga Amurkawa a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2&1 kan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a wasan kwallon kafa hudu sannan suka sake doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy a wasan 4&3 a wasan kwallon kafa hudu da suka rasa a ramukan biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya da ta rage maki hudu ta kai wasan kai tsaye, ko da yake a matsayin mai tsaron ragar kungiyar Furyk kawai ta buƙaci zane don riƙe kyautar.
Bayan sun kasance a matsayi na biyu na kwana biyu, harin na ranar Lahadi ya zama kamar ba za su iya kaiwa ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba zai yiwu ba a yi watsi da makaman ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa ya haifar da rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyar ta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na hukumar duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai masu kyau" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rufe wuraren gwajin nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin ba da damar amfani da makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani irin martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za mu iya amincewa da tsaron kasarmu ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba za mu iya yin watsi da makamanmu ba".
Duk da cewa Ri ta yi tir da Koriya ta Arewa kan adawar da Washington ke yi wa tsarin "mataki-mataki" na kawar da makaman nukiliya inda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada saboda ta dauki matakai a hankali, gaskiyar lamarin ta bayyana da muhimmanci saboda ba ta yi watsi da yardar rai kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya ba.
Ri na nufin wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "kawar da nukiliya daga yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya ba da tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma ki amincewa da shawarar sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan 'kafinta' da kuma kara matsin lamba a cikin takunkumin don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da adawa da 'bayyanar karshen yaki,' "in ji Ri.
"Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya raunana mu mafarki ne na waɗanda ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ƙuntatawa da ake yi a kai a kai yana ƙara sa mu shakkar juna".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump da shugaban Amurka ya gabatar ba a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon wannan makon.
Ministan ya ambaci tarurruka uku ne kawai tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Kim Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan bangaren da ke cikin wannan batun dakatarwar ita ce Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, dakatar da makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya ba zai sami matsala ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da aka kai wa Amurka da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba zai yiwu ba bayan da "Majalissar Shugaba" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a cikin aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a wani taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawo karshen shirin nukiliyarta.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi wannan, ya ce "Idan ya dauki shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni biyar - ba shi da mahimmanci".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta ba da lada kan matakan da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya: "Dole ne a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro da himma kuma ba tare da gazawa ba har sai mun sami cikakkiyar, tabbatacciyar kuma tabbatacciyar dakatarwa ta nukiliya".
Majalisar Tsaro ta amince da tsawaita takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin kawar da kudaden da take baiwa shirin nukiliyar da na makamai masu linzami na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, inda ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi a baya ba ta tafi daidai ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa a cikin sa'o'i kadan bayan haka ta yi masa kashedi kan yin "takunkumi kamar na 'yan daba".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a ganawar da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan cewa za ta bayyana wuraren da take amfani da makaman nukiliya da kuma wuraren da take amfani da su idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da Kim ke nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma komawa ga daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard sun dauki darasi don samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya ba wa dukkan dalibansa karin barci a kokarin da suke yi na yaki da al'adun da ke kara zama na karatun dare-dare da ke dauke da maganin kafeyin.
Wani malami ya gano cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i a duniya ba sa fahimtar abubuwan da za su taimaka musu su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Mata, ya samar da wani darasi da ya yi imanin shine na farko a Amurka.
Ta samu wahayi zuwa ga fara wannan hanya bayan ta ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshen darasin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce: Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?
Ya ce babu wanda ya taba gaya masa muhimmancin barci - kuma hakan ya ba ni mamaki", in ji ta ga The Telegraph.
An gabatar da wannan kwas din a karon farko a wannan shekarar, yana bayyana wa dalibai game da bukatar samun kyakkyawan barci don taimakawa wajen samun nasara a makaranta da wasanni, da kuma inganta rayuwarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard kuma darektan zartarwa na jami'ar kiwon lafiya ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan kwas ne bayan ta gano cewa dalibanta sun rasa bacci a makon.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani bangare, akwai hoton ɗakin kwanan dalibai, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofi, labule, masu horarwa da littattafai don sanar da su game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar aikin wasanni, da kuma muhimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani ɓangaren kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki da ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke da gumakan hulɗa, sannan kuma ƙarfafa masu halarta suyi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullum.
'Mun san cewa ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda ku ma kuke da hakkin ku san sakamakon shan taba", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adun alfahari na 'yin bacci daddare' sun wanzu, in ji shi, yana mai cewa fasahar zamani da karuwar matsin lamba a kan dalibai na nufin rashin bacci matsala ce mai saurin karawa.
Tabbatar da cewa kana samun isasshen barci, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' na dalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi - har ma don hana kiba, saboda rashin barci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su ci gaba da yunwa.
Raymond So, wani dalibi ne mai shekaru 19 a California wanda ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya dauki darasi a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya bude idanunsa kuma ya karfafa masa gwiwa ya fadada shi a fadin harabar makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, ya yi fatan, shi ne neman dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatun digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin koyo kafin su shiga wata cibiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da amfani da agogon ƙararrawa kafin da kuma bayan barci, kuma su san haɗarin tasirin 'hasken shuɗi' da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya lalata sautin circadian daga motsi, yana haifar da matsalar bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: kwallo ta doke 'yan wasan Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala wani rashin nasara a gida lokacin da Dolly Menga ta ci raga ta hanyar daidaita ragamar Steven Gerrard da 1-0 a Livingston.
Har yanzu dai kungiyar Ibrox na neman nasarar farko a hannun abokan hamayyarta tun bayan nasarar da suka samu a St Johnstone a ranar 4 ga watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta ba Gerrard kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 da ya buga a matsayin manajan domin sa ta rasa maki takwas a bayan kungiyar ta Ladbrokes, Hearts.
Amma a minti bakwai kafin farkon rabin wasan, sai aka yi ta fashewa, kuma Rangers ba su da wata hanyar daidaitawa.
Tare da Rangers yanzu a matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa mataki na uku kuma yana baya ne kawai a bayan Hibernian ta hanyar raga.
Kuma 'yan wasan Rangers na iya fuskantar wata matsala bayan da mai tsaron ragar Calum Spence ya samu rauni a kai bayan da aka jefa masa wani abu daga yankin.
Gerrard ya yi musayar takwas a tawagarsa da ta kai wasan kusa da na karshe a gasar Betfred bayan da ta doke Ayr.
Holt ya ci gaba da kasancewa a kan wannan tawagar kamar Livi 11 wanda ya ci kwallo daya daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma ya yi farin ciki da yadda tawagar ta taka leda.
Rangers na iya zama a kan wasan amma Livingston ya yi ƙoƙari ya ci gaba da ci.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo bayan minti biyu da buga kwallon kafa inda Menga ya fara buga kwallon da ya ba Scott Pittman ta hanyar Allan McGregor amma dan wasan ya rasa.
Keaghan Jacobs ya buga kwallo daga baya ya samu kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin hamayyarsa Alan Lithgow ya samu damar buga kwallon ne kawai a bayan raga.
Rangers sun sake karɓar iko amma sun kasance masu bege a cikin minti talatin na ƙarshe.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji ya kamata a ba shi bugun bugun daga kwallo a minti 45 lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo amma alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya ba da damar da dan wasan Colombia ya yi.
Rangers sun samu nasarar buga kwallo biyu a farkon rabin wasan amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly ya yi nasarar kawar da bugun Lassana Coulibaly da kuma bugun Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da cewa Livi ta fara kwallo a minti na 34 ta iya sabawa yanayin wasan, babu wanda zai iya musanta damar da suke da ita.
Har ila yau, 'yan wasan sun kasa fuskantar shirin Jacobs.
Scott Arfield ya yi tsayayya da Declan Gallagher wanda ya ba da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson wanda ya ba da shi ga Menga don kammalawar sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi musayar a lokacin hutu ta hanyar musayar Coulibaly ga Ryan Kent kuma ya kusan yin tasiri nan take lokacin da dan wasan ya ba da kwallon ga Morelos amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya fito daga cikin filin don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da wahalar da abokan hamayyarsa don yin wasan da suke jin daɗi, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna aikawa da nisa bayan nesa.
Ya kamata kungiyar Holt ta kara nisa a zagayen karshe amma McGregor ya kare sosai don ya musanta Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya rasa daga kusurwar.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya nemi karin fanareti yayin da ya yi karo da Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya yi watsi da shi.
Kalanda: Wanda ya kirkiro lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu, shafi na ranar Lahadi da safe: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata a yau, kuma a KARANTA... ranar da aka haifi mai yiwuwa masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da kuma auna radiyo, wani bincike wanda ya haifar da na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
A matsayin babban tushe na kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama kashin bayan al'adun pop, kamar yadda yake a cikin fim din "Bells of Coronado" a 1950, wanda taurari ba a san shi ba Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger counter, wanda ake amfani dashi don gano ma'adanai masu rediyo, kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa wannan kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin atomatik da ke cikin ma'adinai".
Evans: "Haka ne, yana da kyau yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya sa sunansa ya ci gaba da wanzuwa.
