Kanye West ya halarci taron karawa juna sani na Trump, yana sanye da hat na MAGA, bayan ya fito a SNL.
Ba a karɓa sosai ba
An yi wa Kanye West ba'a a cikin studio a lokacin Asabar da dare Live bayan wani babban wasan kwaikwayon inda ya yaba wa Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai yi takara a 2020.
Bayan gabatar da waƙar ta uku a daren da ake kira Ghost Town inda ta sanya kwalliyar Make America Great, ta ci gaba da adawa da 'yan Democrat kuma ta sake maimaita goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Na tambayi fararen fata sau da yawa kuma sun ce, 'Ta yaya za ku goyi bayan Trump, shi ɗan wariyar launin fata ne?'
Idan na damu game da wariyar launin fata, na bar Amurka da dadewa", in ji ta.
SNL ta fara wasan kwaikwayon tare da zane-zane wanda Matt Damon ya yi a cikinsa inda tauraron Hollywood ya kalli furcin Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a buga shi ba, an buga bidiyon Kanye West a shafukan sada zumunta ta hanyar ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock.
Ba mu san ko Rock yana ƙoƙarin yi wa West ba'a da wannan saƙon ba.
Har ila yau, West ya yi korafi ga masu sauraro cewa yana da matsala a bayan fage game da hat.
"Suna cin mutuncina a bayan fage.
Sun ce, "Kada ka fita da wannan hat".
Suna zaluntar ni!
Sai suka ce, "Ni a wani wuri ne da ba shi da muhimmanci", in ji shi, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya kara da cewa, "Za ka so ka ga wannan matsayi marar muhimmanci?" ya ce zai "sa mayafin Superman na, domin hakan na nufin ba za ka iya yi mini ja-gora ba.
