An kawo West ne a matsayin mai maye gurbin mawaƙan Ariana Grande, inda tsohon saurayinta, mawaki Mac Miller ya mutu kwanaki da suka gabata.
West ya ba da mamaki ga mutane da yawa tare da wasan kwaikwayon I Love it, wanda ya yi kama da Perrier Bottle.
West ya samu goyon baya daga shugaban kungiyar masu ra'ayin mazan jiya ta TPUSA, Candace Turner wanda ya aika da sakon: "Ga daya daga cikin mutane masu karfin zuciya: Na gode maka saboda adawa da masu sukar ka".
