Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Kit Harington ya yi amfani da maza mai guba
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO na zamani na wasan kwaikwayo, Game of Thrones.
Amma jarumin, mai shekara 31, ya yi watsi da ka'idar jarumi mai suna Maco, yana mai cewa halayensa da ake nunawa a allon suna nufin matasa suna jin kamar suna bukatar su kasance masu karfi don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, kuma 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'mai karfi' game da magance matsalar.
'Ina jin da karfi sosai a cikin mutum, a wannan lokacin - inda muke da laifi tare da masculinity? 'in ji shi.
'Me muka koya wa maza lokacin da suka girma, dangane da matsalolin da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama sanadin karuwar namiji mai guba saboda halayensa na maza.
Ya daɗa: 'Menene yanayi da kuma abin da aka koyar?
Mene ne ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan tituna, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su zama maza?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a wannan lokaci - ta yaya zamu canza shi?
Domin babu shakka akwai abin da ba daidai ba da samari a yau.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani abu ba game da Game of Thrones lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana cewa ya 'ƙare da fagen fama da dawakai.
A watan Nuwamba, Kit za ta fito da fim din sake fasalin True West na Sam Shepard wanda shine labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, ɗan fashi.
Actor din ya bayyana kwanan nan cewa ya yi la'akari da haduwa da matarsa, Rose, shine mafi kyawun abin da ya faru a Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a wannan shirin, don haka ta haka ne, ya ba ni iyali na gaba kuma rayuwata ta fara daga nan,' in ji shi.
Rose ta ɗauki matsayin Ygritte, ƙaunataccen Jon Snow wanda Kit ya buga, a cikin wannan jerin almara na Emmy.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie na iyali a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar sabbin masu cutar da kashi 14%
China ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin dari na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 aka samu a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar suna kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon shan cutar jini.
Amma adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ta hanyar wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun fada a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau a kasar Sin ya karu da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
A shekarar 1997, an dakatar da aikata laifukan luwadi a kasar Sin, amma ana ganin nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi na kara karuwa.
Saboda tsattsauran ra'ayi na kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da ke da jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin dangantaka.
Tun a shekarar 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
