Labour nafi shirya domin Birtaniya aiki hudu days a mako amma biya ga biyar
Shugaban jam'iyyar Labour, Jeremy Corbyn yana duba wani tsari mai matukar muhimmanci wanda zai ga 'yan Birtaniya suna aiki kwanaki hudu a mako - amma ana biyansu kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu don su samu damar samun kudin shiga.
Za a ga ma'aikata suna jin daɗin ƙarshen mako na kwana uku - amma har yanzu suna dawowa gida da albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyar ta ce wannan ra'ayi ya yi daidai da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ta dauka na ganin an yi amfani da kasar wajen tallafawa ma'aikata.
An yi amfani da shi a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su yi amfani da canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban majiya a jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: 'Ana sa ran za a sanar da binciken manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
'Ba za a yi hakan ba cikin dare amma yin aiki kwana hudu a mako rana ce da ta dace da burin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki da kuma ba da gudummawa ga ma'aikata da kuma dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar baki daya.'
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, tare da Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin mako-mako na kwana hudu a yakin neman zabe a shekarar 2017.
Duk da haka, wannan burin ba shi da goyon baya daga Labour a matsayin cikakke.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: 'Aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce kuma jam'iyyar ba ta la'akari da hakan ba.'
Shugaban majalisa mai zaman kansa, John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron ma'aikatan a makon da ya gabata wajen gabatar da ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar kwace iko daga hannun 'shugaban da ba shi da fuska' da kuma 'masu rikodin' a kamfanonin samar da kayayyaki.
Shadow chancellor shirin kuma yana nufin, masu hannun jari na yanzu a cikin kamfanin ruwa bazai iya dawo da dukkan hannun jarin su ba saboda gwamnatin Labour na iya yin 'yanci' bisa dalilin da suka yi la'akari da aikata laifi.
