Sarah Palin ta nuna rashin lafiyar PTSD Track Palin a taron Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan da ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata a gida a ranar Litinin da daddare.
"Abin da ɗana ya fuskanta, bayan na dawo gida, zan iya jin yadda sauran iyalai ke ji game da wannan matsalar ta PTSD da waɗanda suka dawo gida da rauni", in ji ta a wani taron jama'a don Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ya ce abin da ya faru da 'yarta shi ne "wani abu mai mahimmanci" kuma ya ce game da ɗansa da sauran tsoffin mayakan yaƙi kamar, "sun dawo daban, suna da ƙarfi kuma suna mamakin ko za a yaba musu saboda sadaukarwar da suka yi wa ƙasar".
