Jihohi 18 da Washington sun goyi bayan dokar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan yin watsi da manufar Amurka da ke hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga hare-haren 'yan ta'adda ko ta'addanci na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun yi rajistar abokantaka a gaban kotu a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa wani mai neman mafaka da ya yi adawa da wannan manufar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara ba a cikin shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar 'yancin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta game da manufofin tarayya.
Ya ce, matarsa da 'ya'yanta masu aikata ta'addanci sun yi mata garkuwa amma jami'an Amurka sun yi watsi da bukatar da ta yi ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama shi a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara a jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, da ke da mafi yawan masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fama da matsalolin ƙungiyoyi da kuma tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta sake dawo da hukuncin da aka yanke a 2014 inda Hukumar Kula da 'Yan Gudun Hijira ta ba da izinin masu gudun hijirar da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Karl Racine, Babban Lauyan District of Columbia ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar dokar "ba ta maye gurbin dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa da suka wanzu shekaru da yawa da suka gabata".
Dokar tarayya ta bukaci dukkan aikace-aikacen neman mafaka da a yanke hukunci a kan hujjoji da kuma yanayin da ya haifar da wannan aikace-aikacen, kuma hana shi zai sabawa wannan ka'idar, a cewar wata sanarwa da abokinsa ya yi wa kotun.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kuma yi jayayya da cewa dokar hana shigowar bakin haure za ta lalata tattalin arzikin Amurka inda suka ce masu shigowa da su za su iya zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma ma'aikata.
Babban mai gabatar da kara Jeff Sessions ya umarci alkalin shige da fice da ya dakatar da bai wa wadanda suka tsere daga aikata laifukan tashin hankali a gida da kuma na kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda mafaka a watan Yuni.
Za a bai wa 'yan gudun hijira wadanda suka bar gidajensu saboda tsoron zalunci saboda launin fata, launin fata, kasa ko kuma saboda kasancewa cikin wasu kungiyoyin zamantakewa ko kuma bin wasu ka'idojin siyasa, "in ji Sessions lokacin da ya sanar da manufar a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a nufin mafaka ta magance dukkan matsalolin da mutane ke fuskanta a duniya a kullum, ko da yake dukansu suna da tsanani.
