Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana yadda cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ke da kyau, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi kasar Sin da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi nuni ga tallan da jaridar China Daily ta biya a jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ta zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisa a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya bayyana abin da jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters a matsayin sabon mataki a yakin neman matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
A matsayin al'ada ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallata tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani tare da sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa.
Matakin farko da China ta dauka a yakin cinikayya shi ne, ta yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican da Trump ke wakiltarta, in ji masana harkokin waje na Amurka da China.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babbar mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin ya ce matakin Beijing ya damu da ma'aikata da manoma da kuma kamfanonin Amurka.
China, a cewar Branstad a wani rubutu a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, ta kara zalunci ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a jaridunmu masu zaman kansu.
"A cikin yada wannan farfaganda, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta amince da 'yancin da Amurka ta yi amfani da shi, al'adar da ta fi mayar da hankali kan' yancin magana da 'yancin manema labarai", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a cikin jaridu a Beijing, akwai karancin muryoyin adawa kuma ba za ku iya ganin ainihin ra'ayin jama'a game da makomar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, wanda ke damuwa saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin cikakken iko da jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kuma kara da cewa, "wani babban jarida a kasar Sin ya ki bayar da shawarar buga labarinsa, duk da cewa bai bayyana wane jarida ba".
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da mata masu jefa kuri'a a zaben tsakiyar shekara saboda labarin Kavanaugh, manazarta sun yi gargadi
Duk da cewa wasu manyan 'yan Republican sun goyi bayan dan takarar Kotun Tarayya Brett Kavanaugh da ke fuskantar zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su jawo martani musamman daga mata, a zaben da ke tafe.
Mutane da yawa sun yi farin ciki da wannan labarin kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun ce za su ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Abubuwa ba za su iya canzawa ba, "in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a kimiyyar siyasa daga Cibiyar Nazarin Maxwell, Jami'ar Syracuse a cikin wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar a jaridar The Hill.
Reeher bai gamsu da matakin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya dauka na tilasta wa FBI ta fara bincike ba zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba gobe kuma ba a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kasa na kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ihu November zai zo! yayin da suke zanga-zanga a farfajiyar ginin Majalisar Dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke iko da Kwamitin Shari'a suka zabi ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, in ji Mic.
"Jami'ar dimokiradiyya da kwarin gwiwar za su fashe", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa mai zaman kansa ga shafin labarai.
Mutane suna cewa wannan abu ne mai girma; gaskiya ne.
Wannan zai iya zama mafi girma musamman ga mata masu jefa kuri'a da za su kada kuri'a daga yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, wadanda ba sa son shugaban kasa kuma ba sa yawan kada kuri'a.
Kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana dalla-dalla game da zargin cin zarafin da wani dan takarar Kotun Tarayya ya yi mata, manazarta sun yi tsammanin za a yi gagarumin tashin hankali idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da hakan.
"Wannan abu ne mai matukar wahala ga 'yan jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steela, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma zaben karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh ya yi nasara wajen zama alkalin tarayya, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican ke bi da wannan batu da kuma yadda suke bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil darektan Priorities USA wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zabar 'yan Democrat zuwa ga manema labarai.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amirka sun rabu biyu kuma ba su san wanda za su amince da shi ba a cikin shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh tare da fiye da rabin goyon bayan Ford.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari sun ce za su amince ko kuma za su amince da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun amince ko kuma za su amince da Kavanaugh.
A wani ɓangare kuma kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh zai iya ko ya yi ƙarya a shaidar da ya bayar, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka faɗi haka game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya matsa, FBI yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma aƙalla wasu zarge-zarge, in ji Deborah Ramirez, jaridar The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya yi ikirarin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi lalata da ita a lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya kuma ce dan takarar kotun tarayya ya nuna al'aurarsa a gaban Ford a wani biki lokacin da yake kara a Jami'ar Yale a shekarun 1980.
Masu kirkirar gidan yanar gizo na duniya sun shirya kafa sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da zata iya gasa da Google da Facebook
Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, Tim Berners-Lee ya kaddamar da wani kamfani mai farawa don gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne mai amfani da tushen buɗe tushen tushen software mai ƙarfi wanda Berners-Lee ya ƙirƙira.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai sami damar samun bayanai.
A wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi barkwanci cewa ainihin manufar Inrupt shine "mamaye duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi wannan yanzu", in ji shi game da wannan kamfani.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid wanda ke bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar kayan adana bayanan kan layi na kansu ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan yau da kullun, kalandarku, jerin waƙoƙin ku da sauran kayan aikin ku na musamman.
Yana da kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda kuma suna aiki a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da adana bayanai a cikin wannan bayanan sirri shi ne cewa yana da mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar irin bayanan da ake buƙata.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "mallakar sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar wannan Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shine kawo wasu albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa don taimakawa mutane su more Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ya saya, wasu ma'aikatan masu ci gaba da aka ƙulla su yi aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu rubuta lambar son rai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu ba tare da kasancewa a cikin kowane wuri ba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko ba za su gabatar da wani canji ba wanda zai canza dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su nan take.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A cikin wani labarin a Medium a ranar Asabar, Bernes-Lee ya rubuta, Inrupt, aikinta shine samar da wutar lantarki da tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sababbin shafukan yanar gizo da aka gina ta amfani da Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza duniyar Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya yi ta muhawara da karfi game da bukatar yanar gizo ta zama mai zaman kanta.
Yayin da yake ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance a matsayin Founder da Daraktan Consortium na Yanar Gizo na Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina matukar fatan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Firist Wanda ya karbi Victoria Cross na yakin duniya na farko
Wani limami na cocin Ingila wanda ya karbi lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin soja mai yaki an yi masa bikin a garinsu bayan shekaru 100.
Lt. Colonel Benard Vann wanda ya karbi wannan lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a cikin hare-haren da aka yi a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi ne daga wani mai harbi kwanaki hudu bayan haka kuma bai san cewa ya san cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma ta sojojin Birtaniya ba.
An kafa wani dutse na tunawa da kuma bude labule ta wurin jikoki biyu a cikin wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann ya ce wannan "alama ce mai ban mamaki" domin dutsen zai buɗe labule a cika shekaru 100 da jarumin kakansa.
A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci bataliyarsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin wanda ke cike da hazo mai yawa kuma ya fuskanci mummunan harin bindiga.
Daga nan sai ya bi ta kan iyakar kuma tare da "jarumtaka ta musamman" ya jagoranci shi kafin ya bi ta da bindiga daya kuma ya harbe mutane uku.
An kashe wani dan jarida ne a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba na 1918 - wata daya kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da ba zan iya maimaitawa ba kuma yana da ban sha'awa sosai".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma ajiye furanni bayan bikin wanda aka jagoranci ta hanyar Brentwood Imperial Youth Orchestra.
Michael Vann ya ce "naji daɗin kasancewa cikin wannan zanga-zangar" kuma ya kara da "gaskiya mai ƙarfi tare da goyon bayan da mutane da yawa suka bayar".
