An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
Rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta karbi sabon jirgin ruwan ta a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin jiragen yakin zamanin Cold War, amma ba za a kammala jirgin ba sai shekara mai zuwa saboda lalacewar tsarin da kuma karuwar kudaden, a cewar rahotannin kafofin yada labarai na gida.
An jinkirta karbar jirgin ruwan Rhineland-Pfalz, jirgin farko a karkashin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigate brand har zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton kakakin soja.
An yi alkawarin cewa za ta shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma sai dai matsaloli suka taso a bayan da aka kawo ta.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da aka ba da umarnin ta Navy a 2007 za su maye gurbin jirgin ruwan Bremen.
An fahimci, zai ƙunshi fasali kamar manyan bindigogi, kayan aiki da yawa na anti-tsuntsaye da anti-tsuntsaye da kuma wasu abubuwan ɓoyewa kamar rage radar, hasken wuta da ƙarfin sauti.
Sauran muhimman siffofi sune tsawon lokaci na tsawon lokaci - wannan sabon jirgin ruwa ya kamata ya iya tafiya har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin.
Duk da haka, matsaloli da dama sun nuna cewa wannan jirgin ruwa mai mahimmanci wanda aka ce zai iya nuna ikon Jamus a kasashen waje - zai zama tsoho a lokacin da jirgin ya shiga aikin Navy, a cewar Die Zeit
Wannan jirgin ruwan mai suna F125 ya zama babban labari a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da jami'an sojin ruwan Jamus suka ki amincewa da dawo da jirgin ruwan zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss na Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da jirgi ga magininsa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma jaridar Jamus ta ce wasu matsaloli a cikin software da na'urori sun sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani ga aikin yaki.
An yi la'akari da lalacewar software saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki ne kawai da 120 na'urori - rabin abin da ake bukata don sarrafa tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Akwai kuma batun da ya nuna cewa jirgin ya yi nauyi sosai kuma hakan zai rage aikinsa kuma ya rage ikon sojin ruwan na yin wasu ci gaba a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa jirgin ruwan mai nauyin tan 7,000 na Rheinland-Pfalz ya ninka nauyin jirgin ruwan da sojojin Jamus suka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga lalacewar na'urar, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horo ga masu aikin - shima lamari ne.
Ana cewa an kashe kudin Euro biliyan 3.1 ($3.6bn) - wanda ya karu daga kudin Euro biliyan 2.2 da aka fara.
Wannan matsala da ta addabi jiragen ruwan yakin Jamus ta nuna cewa sojojin Jamus sun kasa.
Tun a farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro a majalisar dokokin kasar ya ce sojojin ruwa na fama da karancin jiragen ruwa masu aiki.
Jami'in ya kuma ce matsalar ta kara muni, saboda tsoffin jiragen yakin da aka dakatar ba su da sabbin jiragen ruwa.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
