Ronaldo ya musanta zargin fyade yayin da lauyoyinsa ke shirin kai karar wata mujallar Jamus.
Cristiano Ronaldo ya ce zargin fyade da ake yi masa "labarai ne na karya" kuma ya ce wasu suna son "inganta kansu" ta amfani da sunansa.
Lauyanta zai kai karar jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus wadda ta wallafa wannan zargi.
An zargi dan wasan gaba na Portugal da Juventus da fyade kan wata Ba'amurke, mai suna Kathryn Mayorga, a dakin otal din Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
Daga bisani an ce ya biya dala 375,000 don rufe bakin wanda aka kashe a cewar rahoton Der Spiegel a ranar Juma'a.
Da yake magana a wani bidiyo na Instagram Live ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 sa'o'i kadan bayan da aka kawo rahoton zargin, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya yi tir da rahoton a matsayin labaran karya.
Wannan ba gaskiya bane.
Abin da suka fada a yau karya ne, in ji mai lashe kyautar Ballon d'Or sau biyar a gaban kyamarar.
