"Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma komai yana da kyau", in ji dan wasan yana murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin kai karar De Spiegel kan zargin, wanda suka kira "wani rahoto mara tushe da kutsawa cikin sirrinsa", a cewar Reuters.
Lauyan dan wasan, Christian Schertz ya ce dan wasan zai nemi diyya kan "lalacewar dabi'a da ta shafi mutuncinsa kai tsaye, wanda zai iya zama daya daga cikin manyan cin zarafin sirri a cikin 'yan shekarun nan".
Wannan lamarin ya faru ne a watan Yunin 2009 a wani babban dakin otal din Palms da Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a wani gidan rawa, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma dakin otal din dan wasan, inda aka zarge shi da wucewa ta hanyar matar ba tare da izini ba, a cewar takardun binciken da aka shigar a Kotun Clark District a Nevada.
