Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
A rashin tsarin sadarwa, hukumomi ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala, yankin arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan da bala'in ya afku.
Ga wasu manyan bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙanƙanin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar kasa da tsunami.
Donggala yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) daga gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin gwamnati, yanki ne na yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da kiwo sune kashin bayan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na Nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a yankin, amma an mayar da hankali ne kawai a Morowali, a bakin tekun da ke daura da Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga Tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane 9.
Indonesia tana cikin yanayin girgizar kasa a cikin Pacific Circle kuma ana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Acheh, Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a duk fadin tekun Indiya, rabin adadin a Aceh.
2005: Wata guguwar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku a kusa da Kota Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa ɗayan tsibiran Mentawai, a Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai matsakaici ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Acheh, ta haifar da barna da firgici, tana tunatar da mazauna yankin game da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka haifar a lokacin, amma sama da mutane 100 suka mutu sakamakon rushewar ginin.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wannan lokacin.
An Kama Sara Palin Kanin 'Yar Aikinta
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska dan takarar shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata harin cikin gida, da hana bayar da rahoton aikata laifukan ta'addanci na cikin gida da kuma adawa da kamewa, a cewar rahoton da jami'an sojin jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, yayin da abokin matar ya yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don kai rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun matar.
An tsare Palin a gidan da ake tsare da shi a Mat-Su, kuma an ba ta belin da ba a biya ba, a kan dala 500.
An gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya yi ikirarin "ba shi da laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da ikirarin, in ji cibiyar.
Palin tana fuskantar manyan laifuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin za ta iya fuskantar ɗaurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake iya yankewa hukuncin kisa da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zargi matashi da kai hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don kai rahoton zargin da ake yi mata.
An gabatar da wannan shari'ar a kotun sojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da aikata harin cikin gida, da hana rahoton aikata laifukan ta'addanci na cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Abokin Palin ya ce mutumin ya buge ta a fuska.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka daga cikin rukunin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 bayan da ta danganta mummunan halin da ɗanta ya yi da PTSD sakamakon hidimarsa a Iraki.
