Masu gabatar da kara sun bukaci a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa
Mai gabatar da kara a New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba zartar da shi ba a jihar da ake kira don aikata laifuka na tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan Babbar hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, yana murkushe masu tafiya da masu hawan keke a hanyarsa a ranar Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "ya yi niyyar" kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma "ya yi niyyar" sanya mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka yi da niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a gundumar Kudancin, New York.
An yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuka biyu, a cewar takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22 ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai saboda ayyukan haram, wanda masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi a lokuta masu aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin ta'addanci da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "tsare-tsare da kuma shiri mai kyau", a cewar mai gabatar da kara, ya bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da aikin a matsayin "mai zalunci, mai zalunci da kuma cin mutunci".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, azaba, da asarar dangi da abokai Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cewar sanarwar da aka yi da niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Kusan lokaci ya yi da gundumar kudancin New York ta fara shari'ar hukuncin kisa.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An yanke hukuncin kisa ga Rosenberg biyu ta hanyar amfani da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan Uzbekistan, ya ce bai yi laifi ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin bisa ga takardun kotu.
Ya bayyana wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da aka yi, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya ce ya yi wannan harin ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayar sa, a cewarsa.
Ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin asibiti, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke kare Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da ake yi.
"Mun ji cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin kisa na rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba, kawai ya kara wa duk wadanda ke da hannu cikin lamarin rauni", a cewar Patton.
A baya, masu kare Saipov sun bukaci masu gabatar da kara da su guji neman hukuncin kisa.
A cewar dan majalisar wakilai na Tory, Nigel Farage ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit.
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin za ta 'sarrafa sojojin jama'a' a yau yayin zanga-zangar a taron 'yan Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su 'ji tsoron' 'yan gurguzu - saboda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisa Theresa May, ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a ba ta alhakin gudanar da shawarwari tare da EU.
Dan majalisar wakilai mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya shaida wa masu zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta 'fita yanzu' idan Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta shi ne warware rikicin da ke tsakanin 'yan majalisa masu goyon bayan Tories da suka shiga zanga-zangar Brexit a birnin.
Firaministan kasar na kokarin tabbatar da cewa shirin Chequers ya ci gaba da aiki a yayin da ake kai hare-hare daga masu goyon bayan ficewa daga EU.
Al'ummar May sun dage kan ci gaba da tattaunawa da Brussels duk da tasirin da ke tattare da ita - da kuma ikon masu shakka game da Turai da ma'aikatan aiki don zaɓar tsakanin kunshin ta ko 'rikice-rikice'.
Bone ya gaya wa taron cewa fita yana nufin fita a Solihull wanda ake kira "Jear Chequers".
Ya bada shawarar Farage ya zama mai daraja kuma ya ba da alhakin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Idan ya aka bai wa wannan alhakin, za mu kasance daga yanzu,' ya ce.
'Na goyi bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu zubar da Chequers.'
Da yake nuna rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi a yakin duniya don zama bayi ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Bone ya yi watsi da shawarar cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin da aka kada kuri'ar 2016: 'Tunanin cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son zama ba daidai ba ne.'
Tory Brexit mai goyon baya, Andrea Jenkyns wanda ya halarci gangamin, ya shaida wa manema labarai cewa: 'Ina cewa kawai: Firayim Minista, saurari muryar mutane.
'Chequers ba su da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'Yan adawa ba za su goyi bayan su ba, ba su da kyau a jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutuka da ke kan tituna da suka zabe mu.
Don Allah ku sauke Chequers ɗin ku fara sauraro".
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa May, ya kara da cewa: 'Firai ministan za ta ci gaba da rike mukaminta idan ta cika alkawarin da ta dauka.'
Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su 'ji dadi' idan suna son cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
'Yanzu wannan amana ce tsakanin mu - jama'a - da kuma siyasa,' in ji shi.
'Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan don gaya musu 'ba za mu bari su tafi ba ta hanyar yin hakan.'
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa masu sauraro masu farin ciki ya kara da cewa: 'Ina so ku sanya ajin siyasarmu, wanda ya kusa cin amanar Brexit, don jin daɗin abin da yake ciki.
"Muna shirin shirya sojojin da za su ba mu nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun sanya Burtaniya 'yanci, mai cin gashin kanta, mai alfahari".
A halin yanzu, Remainer ya yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin ya yi taro a tsakiyar gari.
Har ma masu fafutuka sun yi amfani da tutar Tories da ke adawa da Brexit bayan ƙaddamar da ƙungiyar a ƙarshen mako.
A lokacin taron, wani dan majalisa mai suna Lord Adonis ya yi ba'a ga 'yan majalisa game da matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta tare da aikace-aikacen jam'iyyar.
'Sun ce za su iya sanya tsarin IT a wurin da duk fasahar da ke tare da Kanada da sauransu, don iyakoki marasa daidaituwa, don cinikayya ba tare da kan iyakoki ba,' in ji shi.
'Wannan duka wasa ne.
Babu wani abu da ake kira Brexit mai kyau,' in ji shi.
