Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya zira kwallo a raga a wasan da Giants suka yi da Dundee
Dundee ta yi nasarar cin nasarar wasanta da kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Elite a ranar Juma'a da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan da aka yi da 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da cin nasara da kwallaye biyu ta hanyar bugun daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita matsayin gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da nasarar Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita maki ga Dundee kafin kwallo biyu daga Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar musu da nasara.
Wannan ne karo na uku da kungiyar Elite ta sha kashi a kakar bana ga tawagar Adam Keefe, wadda ta zo daga kasa don doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da jam'iyyun biyu ke karawa a bana, inda Giants ta lashe wasanninta uku.
Budewa ga Dwyer ya zo a minti na hudu a 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford yana ba da taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti hudu daga baya.
Tare da abin da ya zama kamar lokacin buɗewa, Sullivan ya ɗaga idanun mai masaukin a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya taimaka wa Cownie daidai da 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da nasarar Giants a wasan a lokacin hutu na farko lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a daren a karshen lokaci na farko.
Daga bisani 'yan wasan sun sake haduwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa ta hanyar zura kwallo a 27:37.
